The paper deals with image processing and computer vision techniques for smoke removal in minimally invasive surgery. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves graphics and visualization techniques, which could fall under cs.GR (Computer Graphics). Additionally, the paper uses machine learning algorithms, which could be categorized under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). Finally, the paper involves multimedia processing, which could be categorized under cs.MM (Multimedia).
